*: The normal duration was 15802.1 ms, with the anomaly period duration rising to 81692.5 ms, occurring 2 times.\n\n### Additional Notes\n\n- The delay multipliers in the operations are substantially higher than the threshold (greater than 2.0), indicating significant timing anomalies.\n- Multiple services in the checkout path (shipping and payment) exhibit delays, suggesting a potential systemic disturbance across several service interactions within the checkout process.\n\n### JSON Output\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"latency_spike\",\n    \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->paymentservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->productcatalogservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"ShippingService\",\n      \"reason\": \"latency_spike\",\n      \"evidence\": \"normal_avg_duration: 13942.7 ms, anomaly_avg_duration: 80551.4 ms, occurrences: 5\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"PaymentService\",\n      \"reason\": \"latency_spike\",\n      \"evidence\": \"normal_avg_duration: 12831.4 ms, anomaly_avg_duration: 65752.0 ms, occurrences: 3\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CartService\",\n      \"reason\": \"latency_spike\",\n      \"evidence\": \"normal_avg_duration: 15802.1 ms, anomaly_avg_duration: 81692.5 ms, occurrences: 2\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\nThese components show significant delays that could be contributing to the system faults observed during the specified period. Further analysis and correlation with system logs and resource metrics may be required for a more accurate pinpointing of the root cause."}
